--- close_on_exec= bool    -> bool

Sets a close-on-exec flag.

   f = open("/dev/null")
   f.close_on_exec = true
   system("cat", "/proc/self/fd/#{f.fileno}") # cat: /proc/self/fd/3: No such file or directory
   f.closed?                #=> false

